Package: StatsTools
Type: Package
Title: "A Unified Ecosystem for Statistical Analysis
Version: 3.0.0
Author: Pedro Henrique Theotonio de Mesquita Pacheco
Maintainer: Pedro Henrique Theotonio de Mesquita Pacheco <pedrohmp36@gmail.com>
Description: StatsTools is an R package that integrates a suite of statistical tools
   for comprehensive and efficient analysis. It is designed to provide both convenience
   and precision, allowing users to perform their statistical analyses seamlessly with
   less effort, all within a unified environment optimized for high-quality reporting.
